Subject: {{{collective.name}}}: Your Collective is live!

{{> header}}

<style>
.actions {
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
}
.actions a {
  margin: 5px;
}
img.step {
  margin-top: 5px;
}
ol {
  padding: 0px 20px 5px;
}
li {
  margin: 15px 0px;
  line-height: 1.4;
}
h3 {
  margin-top: 0;
}
.grey {
  color: #AAAEB3;
}
.cover {
  background: url('{{config.host.website}}/static/images/email/confetti.png') no-repeat center center;
  text-align: center;
}
</style>


<div class="cover">

  <img src="{{config.host.website}}/static/images/email/welcome.png" />

  <h1>Welcome {{collective.name}},</h1>

  <h2>Thanks for signing up on Open Collective!</h2>

</div>

<br />
<br />
<br />

<table>
  <tbody>
    <tr class="grey">
      <td valign="top" width="50"><img src="{{config.host.website}}/static/images/email/vertical-line-green.png" width="30" /></td>
      <td valign="top">
        <h3 class="grey">Create</h3>
        <p class="grey">Your Collective {{> linkCollective collective=collective}} has been created. Share this link and start accepting financial contributions: <a href="{{config.host.website}}/{{collective.slug}}">{{config.host.website}}/{{collective.slug}}</a></p>
      </td>
      <td valign="top">
        <img src="{{config.host.website}}/static/images/email/github.signup.step1.png" width="180" />
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr><td colspan="3" height="30"></td></tr>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top" width="50"><img src="{{config.host.website}}/static/images/email/vertical-line-grey.png" width="30"  class="step"/></td>
      <td valign="top">
        <h3>Customize</h3>
        <p>Make this Collective your own! Add a logo, cover image, pick your color, and fill out your About section, by clicking those elements of your page. You can also <a href="{{config.host.website}}/dashboard/{{collective.slug}}">visit your settings</a> to create custom contribution tiers and add more team members. (<a href="https://docs.opencollective.com/help/collectives/customize-collective">learn more</a>).</p>
      </td>
      <td valign="top">
        <img src="{{config.host.website}}/static/images/email/github.signup.step2.png" width="180" />
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr><td colspan="3" height="30"></td></tr>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top" width="50"><img src="{{config.host.website}}/static/images/email/vertical-line-grey.png" width="30"  class="step"/></td>
      <td valign="top">
        <h3>Integrate</h3>
        <p>You can show your contributors on your GitHub README and website and create an embeddable donate button using
          <a href="https://docs.opencollective.com/help/collectives/widgets">widgets</a>, connect your Collective to
          <a href="https://docs.opencollective.com/help/collectives/github-sponsors">GitHub Sponsors</a>, and
          <a href="https://docs.opencollective.com/help/collectives/embed-contribution-flow">embed contributions</a> on
          your website, so people don't have to leave in order to pay. You can also connect Twitter to automatically thank
          contributors, and use webhooks to connect to your Slack or other chat—<a href="https://docs.opencollective.com/help/collectives/integrations">here's how</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </td>
      <td valign="top">
        <img src="{{config.host.website}}/static/images/email/github.signup.step3.png" width="180" />
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr><td colspan="3" height="30"></td></tr>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top" width="50"><img src="{{config.host.website}}/static/images/email/vertical-line-grey.png" width="30"  class="step"/></td>
      <td valign="top">
        <h3>Engage</h3>
        <p>Spread the word! Reach out on social media, post an issue, and directly ask companies who use your tools to support you. <a href="https://docs.opencollective.com/help/collectives/communication">Updates</a> are a great way to let everyone know what their contributions are supporting, and <a href="https://docs.opencollective.com/help/collectives/conversations">Conversations</a> can help you get feedback and ideas. In case you attract any unwanted attention, we also have <a href="https://docs.opencollective.com/help/collectives/moderation">spam and moderation tools</a>.</p>
      </td>
      <td valign="top">
        <img src="{{config.host.website}}/static/images/email/github.signup.step4.png" width="180" />
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr><td colspan="3" height="30"></td></tr>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top" width="50"><img src="{{config.host.website}}/static/images/email/vertical-line-grey.png" width="30"  class="step"/></td>
      <td valign="top">
        <h3>Receive and Spend Money</h3>
        <p>If you're looking for tips on fundraising, check out <a href="https://blog.opencollective.com/ten-steps-to-successful-open-source-crowdfunding/">Ten Steps to Open Source Crowdfunding</a>, and if you're looking for ideas about spending it, read <a href="https://blog.opencollective.com/has-your-open-source-community-raised-money-heres-how-to-spend-it/">
          Has Your Open Source Community Raised Money? Here’s How to Spend It</a>. When you're ready to pay out from your Collective, <a href="https://docs.opencollective.com/help/expenses-and-getting-paid/submitting-expenses">submit an expense</a>.</p>
      </td>
      <td valign="top">
        <img src="{{config.host.website}}/static/images/email/github.signup.step5.png" width="180" />
      </td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<br />
<br />
<br />

